# Security headers for the Custos UI (served by Cloudflare Pages).
#
# frame-ancestors: deliberately restrictive. The demo can be embedded
# only by the marketing site and nowhere else. Without this, any site
# can iframe the demo and burn Andrew's API budget under their branding.
#
# NOTE: 'self' alone is NOT sufficient here. 'self' resolves to whichever
# origin served the document (custos.andrewbolaji.com or demo.aintellectsolutions.com),
# so it does not authorize the AIntellect marketing page to frame it.
# The marketing origins must be listed explicitly.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://aintellectsolutions.com https://www.aintellectsolutions.com
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
